GASTROSTOMY TUBE REPLACEMENT NOTE

Immediately prior to procedure a "time out" was called to verify the correct patient,site, procedure, equipment, and support staff. 

Indications for this procedure as well as risks, benefits and alternatives were discussed with patient who provided consent and agreed to proceed. 

